    file uses n_a = N_total (465044 = all cells), so the identity
    mapping branch is taken. The map file was generated from the full
    mesh including land cells, not a masked ocean-only SCRIP mesh.
  - frac_b computed from CRS weight sums in build_comm (no PIO read).
  - MPI_IN_PLACE replaced with explicit buffer for safety.
  - ws_send_buf/ws_recv_buf allocated to max(1, needed) for MPI safety.
  - Fill values (abs > 1e10) now zeroed in MPAS-O and MPAS-SI send
    buffer packing before SpMV, matching the EAM pattern.

